data.name: tbHelp.Text
data.value:
[1] To process warrant data, first pull up 'Warrants' in CAD. [2] Open the browser's developer menu and select 'Network'. [3] Reload the page with as many warrants as possible. [4] Select the final GET reply and choose 'Response' on the right side. [5] Right click a response and click 'Copy All'. [5] Save the data to a '.txt' or '.json' file, OR paste it directly in the 'JSON Data' tab. * [6] Select where you want to save the produced spreadsheet and name it ('.xlsx' extension is automatically added). [7] Click "Process" and you are done! *You can save the pasted data to a JSON file using options in the 'JSON Data' tab.
[Process] Tab Check boxes (Open File/Folder When Done) open the output file when the process is completed. (Works for Spreadsheet or JSON Data Output)
